1.title: Las Vegas
1.plot: Rocco Leo Gaglioti, host of Fashion News Live, finds out exactly what is happening with the fashion sense as he highlights the streets of Las Vegas. Will they be "Fashion Able" or will they be "DWI", Dressing Without Instruction?

imdb.title: FNL's Fashion Able
plot: The Host of Fashion _News_ (qv) Live, Rocco Leo Gaglioti hits the streets to find out what people on the streets around the country are wearing. This season we find out what the people on the streets of Las Vegas are (or aren't) wearing.::Anonymous
